reviewText:
I have tried other Wu Xing, 5 Element qigong dvds, but this one has the strangest looking movements and the continuous need to visualize scenes of nature I found to be really annoying. I pressed the ejection button before watching the whole thing.
I feel powerful Qi flow from doing Damon Mitchell's Wu Xing Qigong which you can find on YouTube but to learn how to do it so you will get the benefits you have to have his book, Heavenly Streams, which you can find on Amazon.com.
